metadata.name: Big Red Boot - #001
metadata.description:
Astro Boots act as a nod to Osamu Tezuka's 1951 Tetsuwan-Atomu 鉄腕アトム (Astro Boy) illustrations.

Which, as of February 7, 2023, has seen the footwear of its main character go viral, thanks to a physical reproduction by culture collective MSCHF.

This particular digital work additionally pays homage to the iconic Boots token, created by vector artist Jeremy Booth.

In the words of Astro Boy, "this is it. This is what I was created for. This is my destiny."
